#SmartWaterTwin at the Green Festival in Novi Sad, Serbia.

🌍The #Green #Festival is organized by the #Children's Ecological Academy Association, as unique program for children dedicated to the preservation and protection of the environment.

📢The Green Festival was held from 5-9th June in #NoviSad with the aim of improving the development of environmental awareness among #children aged 6 to 10 through educational workshops and interactive games. After the educational workshops, all children had the opportunity to #play in the area of ​​the Starli Amusement Park from Novi Sad. Support for the implementation of the #Green Festival was provided by partners Starli Amusement Park and Ardagh Metal Packaging Serbia.

💧Our PI, Djurdja Kerkez held a #workshop called “It is time to value water”. Through conversation and interactive games, around 120 children learned about good and bad habits in #water consumption, patterns of #water consumption in the world, but also how we can use purified wastewater.

📚They also calculated their own #water #footprint to realize the value of water for us.

caption:
I played Dinosaur Island again recently and forgot what smooth design it is.

The way the game flows through each stage really helps to teach the game and for everyone to remain competitive.

The catch up mechanism is an interesting one where players need to be doing well, but not too well as the first player goes last in turn order. 

Though I do love that first player marker of a slap bracelet!

So it continues to remain in my collection, for the smoothness of play, interesting theme and top drawer colour palette. 

Could there be more expansions in the future @pandasaurus_games?

New Purchases! The last big haul before, hopefully, new house expenditure (wooo adult life stuff!) and whoa whoa WHOA we have a lot in store! Considering @cartoonsaloon fantastic ‘Wolfwalkers’ was an AppleTV+ exclusive, I was dejected that no physical was to come. But BAM @studiocanaluk came along and put the whole Irish Folklore trilogy out! Love this set, and adore their animation style. Another @arrowvideo limited edition in Cronenberg’s surrealist cult classic ‘Naked Lunch’, which looks interesting to say the least. A plethora of @britishfilminstitute titles from newer release ‘Enys Men’ to some more Ozu classics in ‘Late Spring’. More @eurekaentertainment “Masters of Cinema”? Absolutely, ‘The Quiet Man’ this time. Some outstanding @curzonfilm titles in Haneke’s own remake of ‘Funny Games’ and some Varda delightfulness ‘Faces Places’. What else…what else…oh, another @ukcriterion, a @dazzlermedia release of a bloody entertaining crime mystery and Jodie Foster in a @paramountuk classic. Jeeeez I need a breather after that! - Enys Men

- Late Spring

At the story writing workshop we explored our superpowers and emotions 🎈

"The hardest thing for me in everyday life is watching my blood sugar. My phone often runs out of battery and my mum can't see my blood sugars. ⚽ I like playing football the most, that's what I want to do when I grow up. The symbol for my superpower is the badge on my shirt from my favourite football team. 🟢 I feel most at ease in my room, at home, and green relaxes me," Milan tells us during the workshop. 

✍️ In a relaxed and creative atmosphere, guided by our lovely colleague Paula, the workshop participants played with superpowers and emotions, shared fears and sources of strength, chose and described an object that inspires them, 🖌️ and then wrote and illustrated its story.

📖 We loved being together and letting the stories carry us away!

Melansir dari Polygon, seri ini nantinya akan kembali membawa Kazuma Kiryu, sang tokoh utama yang keluar dari persembunyian setelah memalsukan kematiannya. Di mana ia rela membuang dan meninggalkan masa lalu demi melindungi keluarganya.

Menggunakan codename ‘Joryu”, ia digambarkan sebagai Secret Agent dalam membasmi kekacauan di Sotenbori dan Yokohama. Dalam video yang ditampilkan, Kiryu bakal mempunyai dua fighting style berbeda, yaitu Yakuza dan Agent style.

Bagi yang sudah mengikuti seri game Yakuza sebelumnya, Yakuza style memungkinan pemain menyerang musuh dengan agresif. Sedangkan Agent style menjadi gaya baru di mana Kiryu dapat menyerang musuh dengan serangkaian gadget berteknologi tinggi.

Tambahan lainnya, The Man Who Erased His Name juga menghadirkan beragam mini game di dalamnya. Mini Cabaret, karaoke, balap sirkuit, adu mekanik di arena Castle, dan masih banyak lagi. Game ini juga suguhkan berbagai side quest yang dapat kamu mainkan jika misi utama sudah selesai, hampir sama seperti pada seri – seri Yakuza sebelumnya.

#SmartWaterTwin at the Green Festival in Novi Sad, Serbia.

🌍The #Green #Festival is organized by the #Children's Ecological Academy Association, as unique program for children dedicated to the preservation and protection of the environment.

📢The Green Festival was held from 5-9th June in #NoviSad with the aim of improving the development of environmental awareness among #children aged 6 to 10 through educational workshops and interactive games. After the educational workshops, all children had the opportunity to #play in the area of ​​the Starli Amusement Park from Novi Sad. Support for the implementation of the #Green Festival was provided by partners Starli Amusement Park and Ardagh Metal Packaging Serbia.

💧Our PI, Djurdja Kerkez held a #workshop called “It is time to value water”. Through conversation and interactive games, around 120 children learned about good and bad habits in #water consumption, patterns of #water consumption in the world, but also how we can use purified wastewater.

📚They also calculated their own #water #footprint to realize the value of water for us.

The way the game flows through each stage really helps to teach the game and for everyone to remain competitive.

The catch up mechanism is an interesting one where players need to be doing well, but not too well as the first player goes last in turn order. 

Though I do love that first player marker of a slap bracelet!

So it continues to remain in my collection, for the smoothness of play, interesting theme and top drawer colour palette.

New Purchases! The last big haul before, hopefully, new house expenditure (wooo adult life stuff!) and whoa whoa WHOA we have a lot in store! Considering @cartoonsaloon fantastic ‘Wolfwalkers’ was an AppleTV+ exclusive, I was dejected that no physical was to come. But BAM @studiocanaluk came along and put the whole Irish Folklore trilogy out! Love this set, and adore their animation style. Another @arrowvideo limited edition in Cronenberg’s surrealist cult classic ‘Naked Lunch’, which looks interesting to say the least. A plethora of @britishfilminstitute titles from newer release ‘Enys Men’ to some more Ozu classics in ‘Late Spring’. More @eurekaentertainment “Masters of Cinema”? Absolutely, ‘The Quiet Man’ this time. Some outstanding @curzonfilm titles in Haneke’s own remake of ‘Funny Games’ and some Varda delightfulness ‘Faces Places’. What else…what else…oh, another @ukcriterion, a @dazzlermedia release of a bloody entertaining crime mystery and Jodie Foster in a @paramountuk classic. Jeeeez I need a breather after that! Let’s dig in:
•
- The Accused 
- Enys Men
- Faces Places
- Funny Games
- Kamikaze Hearts
- Late Spring
- The Only Son
- Naked Lunch
- The Outfit
- The Quiet Man
- Repulsion

Irish Folklore Trilogy:
- The Secret of Kells
- Song of the Sea
- Wolfwalkers

At the story writing workshop we explored our superpowers and emotions 🎈

"The hardest thing for me in everyday life is watching my blood sugar. My phone often runs out of battery and my mum can't see my blood sugars. ⚽ I like playing football the most, that's what I want to do when I grow up. The symbol for my superpower is the badge on my shirt from my favourite football team. 🟢 I feel most at ease in my room, at home, and green relaxes me," Milan tells us during the workshop. 

✍️ In a relaxed and creative atmosphere, guided by our lovely colleague Paula, the workshop participants played with superpowers and emotions, shared fears and sources of strength, chose and described an object that inspires them, 🖌️ and then wrote and illustrated its story.

📖 We loved being together and letting the stories carry us away!

Melansir dari Polygon, seri ini nantinya akan kembali membawa Kazuma Kiryu, sang tokoh utama yang keluar dari persembunyian setelah memalsukan kematiannya. Di mana ia rela membuang dan meninggalkan masa lalu demi melindungi keluarganya.

Menggunakan codename ‘Joryu”, ia digambarkan sebagai Secret Agent dalam membasmi kekacauan di Sotenbori dan Yokohama. Dalam video yang ditampilkan, Kiryu bakal mempunyai dua fighting style berbeda, yaitu Yakuza dan Agent style.

Bagi yang sudah mengikuti seri game Yakuza sebelumnya, Yakuza style memungkinan pemain menyerang musuh dengan agresif. Sedangkan Agent style menjadi gaya baru di mana Kiryu dapat menyerang musuh dengan serangkaian gadget berteknologi tinggi.

Tambahan lainnya, The Man Who Erased His Name juga menghadirkan beragam mini game di dalamnya. Mini Cabaret, karaoke, balap sirkuit, adu mekanik di arena Castle, dan masih banyak lagi. Game ini juga suguhkan berbagai side quest yang dapat kamu mainkan jika misi utama sudah selesai, hampir sama seperti pada seri – seri Yakuza sebelumnya.

#SmartWaterTwin at the Green Festival in Novi Sad, Serbia.

🌍The #Green #Festival is organized by the #Children's Ecological Academy Association, as unique program for children dedicated to the preservation and protection of the environment.

📢The Green Festival was held from 5-9th June in #NoviSad with the aim of improving the development of environmental awareness among #children aged 6 to 10 through educational workshops and interactive games. After the educational workshops, all children had the opportunity to #play in the area of ​​the Starli Amusement Park from Novi Sad. Support for the implementation of the #Green Festival was provided by partners Starli Amusement Park and Ardagh Metal Packaging Serbia.

💧Our PI, Djurdja Kerkez held a #workshop called “It is time to value water”. Through conversation and interactive games, around 120 children learned about good and bad habits in #water consumption, patterns of #water consumption in the world, but also how we can use purified wastewater.

📚They also calculated their own #water #footprint to realize the value of water for us.

I played Dinosaur Island again recently and forgot what smooth design it is.

The way the game flows through each stage really helps to teach the game and for everyone to remain competitive.

The catch up mechanism is an interesting one where players need to be doing well, but not too well as the first player goes last in turn order. 

Though I do love that first player marker of a slap bracelet!

So it continues to remain in my collection, for the smoothness of play, interesting theme and top drawer colour palette.

New Purchases! The last big haul before, hopefully, new house expenditure (wooo adult life stuff!) and whoa whoa WHOA we have a lot in store! Considering @cartoonsaloon fantastic ‘Wolfwalkers’ was an AppleTV+ exclusive, I was dejected that no physical was to come. But BAM @studiocanaluk came along and put the whole Irish Folklore trilogy out! Love this set, and adore their animation style. Another @arrowvideo limited edition in Cronenberg’s surrealist cult classic ‘Naked Lunch’, which looks interesting to say the least. A plethora of @britishfilminstitute titles from newer release ‘Enys Men’ to some more Ozu classics in ‘Late Spring’. More @eurekaentertainment “Masters of Cinema”? Absolutely, ‘The Quiet Man’ this time. Some outstanding @curzonfilm titles in Haneke’s own remake of ‘Funny Games’ and some Varda delightfulness ‘Faces Places’. What else…what else…oh, another @ukcriterion, a @dazzlermedia release of a bloody entertaining crime mystery and Jodie Foster in a @paramountuk classic. Jeeeez I need a breather after that! Let’s dig in:
•
- The Accused 
- Enys Men
- Faces Places
- Funny Games
- Kamikaze Hearts
- Late Spring
- The Only Son
- Naked Lunch
- The Outfit
- The Quiet Man
- Repulsion

Irish Folklore Trilogy:
- The Secret of Kells
- Song of the Sea
- Wolfwalkers

At the story writing workshop we explored our superpowers and emotions 🎈

"The hardest thing for me in everyday life is watching my blood sugar. My phone often runs out of battery and my mum can't see my blood sugars. ⚽ I like playing football the most, that's what I want to do when I grow up. The symbol for my superpower is the badge on my shirt from my favourite football team. 🟢 I feel most at ease in my room, at home, and green relaxes me," Milan tells us during the workshop. 

✍️ In a relaxed and creative atmosphere, guided by our lovely colleague Paula, the workshop participants played with superpowers and emotions, shared fears and sources of strength, chose and described an object that inspires them, 🖌️ and then wrote and illustrated its story.

📖 We loved being together and letting the stories carry us away!

Melansir dari Polygon, seri ini nantinya akan kembali membawa Kazuma Kiryu, sang tokoh utama yang keluar dari persembunyian setelah memalsukan kematiannya. Di mana ia rela membuang dan meninggalkan masa lalu demi melindungi keluarganya.

Menggunakan codename ‘Joryu”, ia digambarkan sebagai Secret Agent dalam membasmi kekacauan di Sotenbori dan Yokohama. Dalam video yang ditampilkan, Kiryu bakal mempunyai dua fighting style berbeda, yaitu Yakuza dan Agent style.

Bagi yang sudah mengikuti seri game Yakuza sebelumnya, Yakuza style memungkinan pemain menyerang musuh dengan agresif. Sedangkan Agent style menjadi gaya baru di mana Kiryu dapat menyerang musuh dengan serangkaian gadget berteknologi tinggi.

Tambahan lainnya, The Man Who Erased His Name juga menghadirkan beragam mini game di dalamnya. Mini Cabaret, karaoke, balap sirkuit, adu mekanik di arena Castle, dan masih banyak lagi. Game ini juga suguhkan berbagai side quest yang dapat kamu mainkan jika misi utama sudah selesai, hampir sama seperti pada seri – seri Yakuza sebelumnya.
